05:22.388 --> 05:25.084
It's fucking awesome up there. You going to work?

05:25.391 --> 05:26.949
Where you going?

05:27.660 --> 05:28.820
Ketchikan.

05:29.128 --> 05:30.459
Ketchikan.

05:31.798 --> 05:34.824
It's good for greenhorns. Cooper River
is pretty good, too. Further north.

05:34.967 --> 05:37.401
Lots of work on that slime line.

05:37.537 --> 05:42.406
You should check out Northwestern Fisheries
because their housing is fucking awesome.

05:42.542 --> 05:46.535
Tell Mike Murphy you met me, because he's all right.

05:47.847 --> 05:49.371
Okay, I might. Thanks.

05:49.849 --> 05:51.874
The money's better there, too.

05:52.118 --> 05:55.110
There's no expenses, you know?
You just walk with everything.

05:56.522 --> 05:57.989
Well, whatever you do...

05:58.491 --> 06:01.688
...don't tell Old Man Brutus that you met me.

06:01.894 --> 06:06.524
Because he was a little upset when
I left in somewhat of a hurry.

06:06.699 --> 06:07.996
There was this incident...

06:08.134 --> 06:11.865
...involving me operating a two ton earth mover...

06:12.004 --> 06:14.564
...in a state slightly less than sober.

06:15.408 --> 06:17.535
Some friends of mine...

06:17.844 --> 06:19.106
...they were goofing around...

06:19.412 --> 06:23.542
...and we got the thing started, and
I put it in gear and that was that.

06:23.683 --> 06:26.584
We drove the thing across the construction site.

06:26.719 --> 06:30.450
Getting it to stop, though. No one told me that.

06:30.590 --> 06:32.023
So, we finally had to jump off...

06:32.158 --> 06:34.820
...and the thing just rolled all the
way across the construction site.

06:34.927 --> 06:37.191
We couldn't stop the thing. We tried everything.

06:37.530 --> 06:40.556
It snapped the retaining wires.

06:40.700 --> 06:42.167
Huge spray of sparks.

06:42.535 --> 06:45.595
The Cat went over the hill head over heels...

06:45.738 --> 06:47.831
...ass over tit, right into the water.

06:47.940 --> 06:51.899
It was probably a hundred thousand-dollar piece
of equipment, gone in four fucking seconds.

06:52.044 --> 06:54.478
But they couldn't pin it on me, man, I was gone.

07:22.942 --> 07:24.933
