09:50.089 --> 09:52.751
Yeah, I got it, I got it, okay?

09:55.361 --> 09:58.797
I don't know what it is. It was fine yesterday.

09:59.298 --> 10:02.028
You just gonna have to get it off the property.

10:05.638 --> 10:08.232
Well, where is that? How far is the property?

10:08.374 --> 10:11.810
Street. The street's public. You
just have to get it off the lot.

10:19.852 --> 10:20.944
All right, jump in.

10:45.845 --> 10:46.971
Lu!

10:47.413 --> 10:49.973
What do you know about that...

10:50.149 --> 10:51.878
...station over there?

10:52.151 --> 10:54.949
Seems to get business. A lot of cars come and go.

10:55.121 --> 10:57.248
He's the closest. He's got that going for him.

10:58.290 --> 11:01.418
What about, is there some kind
of grocery store around here?

11:01.727 --> 11:03.422
