broken today, so it's gonna be a while.

16:24.149 --> 16:25.514
Why don't you buy her cans from her?

16:25.684 --> 16:28.175
I don't have any money to buy her cans from her.

16:28.320 --> 16:31.687
But, hey, I tell you what, I'll take those. Hey, dog.

16:31.790 --> 16:35.521
I'll take those from you and
I'll give you the money later.

16:37.196 --> 16:39.323
I mean, you've only got....

16:41.433 --> 16:44.493
