16:44.636 --> 16:46.297
I'll find you later.

16:46.472 --> 16:49.202
Okay, you can just take those. That's fine.

16:49.341 --> 16:51.332
-Are you sure? -Yeah, that's fine.

16:51.510 --> 16:53.239
Hey, thanks. Thanks a lot.

16:53.545 --> 16:55.274
Yeah. That's pretty cool.

16:57.216 --> 16:59.081
Don't bother anybody, okay?

17:00.652 --> 17:02.586
