-Let go of me.

19:23.695 --> 19:27.256
All right, I'm gonna have to ask you
to step inside the store, okay?

19:33.639 --> 19:35.368
Sit here, please.

19:35.507 --> 19:36.906
What's going on, Andy?

19:37.376 --> 19:40.971
This customer neglected to pay for a few items.

19:41.813 --> 19:45.271
I watched the whole thing. I saw
her since she came in the store.

19:46.385 --> 19:47.818
