20:26.425 --> 20:30.418
If a person can't afford dog food
they shouldn't have a dog.

20:30.562 --> 20:31.688
Andy.

20:33.565 --> 20:36.693
Sir, I just made a mistake is all. I'm very sorry.

20:37.035 --> 20:39.435
