20:47.579 --> 20:50.013
We have a policy, ma'am.

21:04.796 --> 21:08.755
Hi, this is Andy Mooney from Jack's on Lombard.

21:28.954 --> 21:32.048
Sir, my dog is tied up out front.

21:35.027 --> 21:37.928
-Sir, my dog is tied up outside.
-Just relax.

21:41.533 --> 21:42.864
