Lucy, come out now!

27:07.192 --> 27:08.921
What are you doing here?

27:09.961 --> 27:12.953
Looking for my dog. She's
gone. I hope you're real happy.

27:14.666 --> 27:16.258
Lucy, come!

27:35.387 --> 27:36.411
Lucy!

27:41.426 --> 27:44.862
Come on, girl. Come on out, girl! Come on, Lu!

27:47.732 --> 27:49.723
