27:55.173 --> 27:57.733
You know, your son is a real hero!

27:58.777 --> 28:00.039
Lucy!

28:00.712 --> 28:02.304
Come now!

28:07.952 --> 28:09.010
Lucy!

28:54.232 --> 28:56.223
Have you seen my dog?

28:57.368 --> 28:59.802
