29:26.064 --> 29:27.258
You all right, honey?

29:30.268 --> 29:32.793
Yeah. I just need to get to the pound now.

29:33.037 --> 29:34.527
Well, that's easy.

29:35.140 --> 29:38.007
You just take the street right here.

29:38.376 --> 29:43.006
Go straight down till it dead ends that way about...

29:43.148 --> 29:46.447
...just right till it dead ends, then
you head right about three miles.

29:47.886 --> 29:49.820
You lose your dog, is that it?

29:49.988 --> 29:50.977
Yeah...

29:53.558 --> 29:55.082
...that's what it looks like.

29:55.293 --> 29:57.887
That's a shame. Somewhere around here?

29:58.863 --> 30:00.455
Yeah, that store.

30:00.598 --> 30:02.065
Jack's?

30:02.801 --> 30:04.393
I'm sure someone's got her.

30:05.837 --> 30:07.828
She couldn't have gotten too far.

30:08.006 --> 30:09.997
