30:10.241 --> 30:13.870
I'm sure it wasn't that long. She'll turn up.

30:18.149 --> 30:19.241
Okay.

30:25.590 --> 30:29.617
So I just go down this street,
and then I take a right?

30:30.128 --> 30:33.529
