31:50.508 --> 31:51.941
<So what's up? >

31:53.678 --> 31:58.274
Nothing. I'm just calling. Just, you know, just....

32:00.151 --> 32:01.448
<Nothing?>

32:04.455 --> 32:06.047
The car broke.

32:07.258 --> 32:10.716
I don't know. It's kind of bad here, actually.

32:13.364 --> 32:15.355
