32:36.020 --> 32:38.181
I don't want anything. I'm just calling.

32:38.323 --> 32:40.257
<I can't talk with everyone on the phone. >

32:40.458 --> 32:43.985
<I'll talk to you when you're
done with Dan. Bye, honey.>

32:45.496 --> 32:47.020
<Everything's all right? >

32:48.466 --> 32:49.763
Yeah. Everything's great.

32:51.302 --> 32:55.295
You kind of sound like you're busy
over there, so I'm gonna call you later.

32:55.473 --> 32:58.135
<All right, if everything's fine. See ya.>

32:58.309 --> 32:59.640
Yeah, see ya, bye.

33:56.701 --> 33:58.134
Lu!

34:05.243 --> 34:06.710
Luce!

34:19.424 --> 34:21.619
I was usually like the only white person there.

34:23.527 --> 34:24.620
That's so weird.

34:24.762 --> 34:26.195
Why does that girl hate you so much?

34:26.397 --> 34:31.164
I saw the cheerleading squad. Madison's
got some chunky cheerleaders.

34:32.737 --> 34:34.795
Dude, fuck, there's a lady in there!

34:35.773 --> 34:37.239
Your mom's always tired.

34:37.408 --> 34:39.739
Yeah, my mom's like, always, always....

34:51.656 --> 34:53.317
